Libyan Rebel Council Says Won’t Offer Qaddafi Exit Guarantees

-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 
2011-03-28T19:35:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/libyan-rebel-council-says-won-t-offer-qaddafi-exit-guarantees.html
Libyan rebels won’t offer Muammar
Qaddafi any guarantees that may allow him to depart  Libya , Abdel
Hafiz Ghoga, a spokesman for the rebel’s interim council, said
today.  “The demands are for this regime to face trial because of
the crimes it has committed against the Libyan people,” he told
Al Jazeera television in an interview from the rebel stronghold
of Benghazi in eastern Libya.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alaa Shahine in Dubai at 
 asalha@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 